moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個hehe都應該試過暗戀直男 <br />\n每個hehe 都渴望被愛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChris 個份覇氣總裁 真係好吸引👨&zwj;❤️&zwj;👨<br />\n不禁幻想 現實中既暗戀對象 <br />\n故事設計得好唯美👬<br />\n我差幾集就大結局啦😢<br />\n睇到Chris 去到澳洲揾到Jasper 得到原諒👨&zwj;❤️&zwj;💋&zwj;👨<br />\n好想知康妮會唔會痴線 會唔會接受唔到而自殺🤦🏻&zwj;♂️😂"},{"pid":"7de4da2b9058d21657801b3c1f3b5a828920ba24","tid":580253,"uid":17388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個結局傷心到"},{"pid":"5012c573a74b904bdcda45e79c6b7641a6bd9fc7","tid":580253,"uid":268756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:38:17.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人翻睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}